{
  "stem": "7093.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "I thought she was Ukrainian, and I-- And the Frenchman used to bring me news.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Somehow the man had always news, and he used to bring me news so I could bring them back the news.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "We always had a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "Most of time there was no control, and we had a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "While I was offloading we could speak to each other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "We're not supposed to, but we could speak to each other since I spoke French, so it was all right.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Now, we-- we were getting weaker and weaker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And what I did not say is that we had-- when we arrived in Hessich-Lichtenau we got a big piece of cloth about this size, white piece of cloth, on which our-- each of our number was printed on in very, very large letters.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And we had to sew that onto our clothing at the back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From that moment on we were numbers, except that I became an individual to the commander because I buried his dog, which was a fantastic thing, I mean, to become and individual again.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were numbers, and anybody who disliked you or some things that you did could denounce you through your number.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody could see from far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We walked to work through two villages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the time we walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes we went by train, but most of the time we walked through two villages so everybody could see us with our shaven head, barefoot in winter, in snow and ice, and even before that.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that when people tell me they didn't know anything, I-- I get very angry because they did know it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't overlook us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in the middle of the town, and they couldn't ignore us.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
